title: Sidewall And Border, ca. 1885
provenance: From a house in Moorefield, West Virginia.
creditline: Gift of J.C. Eisenhart Wall Paper Co.
description: Anglo-Japanesque sidewall and border: a) Sidewall, center motif of terrace with peacock; surrounding it, Japanese decorative motifs. Original gray ground washed off, leaving wrinkled yellow paper as ground; b) border, portrait medallion and urns between border, on yellow ground.

tombstone.epitaph:
Sidewall And Border, ca. 1885.
ca. 1885. Machine-printed. Gift of J.C. Eisenhart Wall Paper Co.. 1964-48-1-a,b.
